Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:05.86,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Try！ 永不放棄的決心 就在這個胸懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:11.36,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}不論何時不曾忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.69,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Don’t cry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:20.67,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}約好了 不要獨自一人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:24.99,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}因為彼此永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:35.22,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}將這份感傷（静靜地承擔下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.40,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}定能變得更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:41.32,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:45.43,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}現在就笑一個吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:47.56,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:56.02,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}這是自己下的決定 並不是他人的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.87,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}用率真的語氣說出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:02.05,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Hello！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:10.31,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}唱著往常的歌曲 將點滴的勇氣灌注於心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:12.10,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Yeah！
